Here is an analysis of the reasons for drop in engagement in Yammer during end August, early September 2014.
I have executed several queries for the analysis.
I have suggested couple of possible rectification steps:
  1. Look at the email functionality
  2. There is possibly some issue with the mobile application

The project is available at :
https://modeanalytics.com/editor/dbandy/reports/6d2a01e4f437

The problem definition is available at :
https://community.modeanalytics.com/sql/tutorial/a-drop-in-user-engagement/
